name: Gaia (Final fantasy XIV) - LoRA - Realistic
description:
Gaia (Final fantasy XIV) - LoRA - Realistic

Final Fantasy 14 is one of my favorite games, I used Never Ending Dream (NED) as a base for training to basically turn a game character Gaia into a real one.

I usually use checkpoint, but more recently I've been using majicmixRealistic_V4, but you can also use NED for 2.5D character pics.

I shared some of my past works on my Twitter page: Change @LianReen, so if you're interested in the Final Fantasy XIV genre, check it out!

Recommended weight 0.6~0.8
